org.encog.examples.neural.predict.sunspot

Class PredictSunspotSVM

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.encog.examples.neural.predict.sunspot.PredictSunspotSVM

  • public class PredictSunspotSVM
extends Object
    This example predicts sunspots using a support vector machine. The sunspot data is from an example by Karsten Kutza, written in C on 1996-01-24. http://www.neural-networks-at-your-fingertips.com
